org.fcrepo.server.journal.readerwriter.singlefile

Class SingleFileJournalReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fcrepo.server.journal.xmlhelpers.AbstractXmlReader

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JournalConstants, SingleFileJournalConstants

    public class SingleFileJournalReader
extends JournalReader
implements SingleFileJournalConstants
    A rudimentary implementation of JournalReader that just reads all entries from a single Journal file.

    Useful only for System tests.

    Author:
    Jim Blake
